	@RefListFont @Font @RefListBreak @Break {
	    @NumberMarker&&preceding @Tagged tag &
	    @PageMark tag
	    |@RefListIndent {label @ListLabel tag} @RefItem {@RefPrint tag}
	    |@RefListRightIndent
